import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Character } from './character.model'; @Component({ selector: 'app-character', templateUrl: './character.component.html', styleUrls: ['./character.component.scss'], }) export class CharacterComponent { public character?: Character; constructor(httpClient: HttpClient) { httpClient .get('http://localhost:8080/api/characters/dusk') .subscribe((data) => { this.character = data as Character; console.log(data); }); } }
